npcText: He looks incredibly pallid, hand clutching his side as his breaths become shallow. You can see a growing red stain bloom from the area he is holding.
Keith: *grunts* Not sure how much you can help, frankly.
Keith: War. Don't think I need to explain.
Keith: No idea. I'm really just glad to be off-duty.
Keith: Weirdly enough, I don't feel that bad. Like, I'm bleeding but I don't actually feel any pain.
